"><summary>方法</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel\"><code>cancel()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/commitStyles\"><code>commitStyles()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish\"><code>finish()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/pause\"><code>pause()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/persist\"><code>persist()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/play\"><code>play()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/reverse\"><code>reverse()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/updatePlaybackRate\"><code>updatePlaybackRate()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Events</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/cancel_event\"><code>cancel</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/finish_event\"><code>finish</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Animation/remove_event\"><code>remove</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>继承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n<p></p><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>非标准:</strong> 该特性是非标准的，请尽量不要在生产环境中使用它！</p></div><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"概述","isH3":true,"content":"<p>Returns the time, in milliseconds since the epoch, at which animations started now should be considered to have started. This value should be used instead of, for example, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Date/now\">Date.now()</a></code>, because this value will be the same for all animations started in this window during this refresh interval, allowing them to remain in sync with one another.</p>\n<p>This also allows JavaScript-based animations to remain synchronized with CSS transitions and SMIL&nbsp;animations triggered during the same refresh interval.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"语法","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>time</em> = window.mozAnimationStartTime;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"规范","isH3":true,"content":"<p>不属于任何规范。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关链接","title":"相关链接","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/requestAnimationFrame\"><code>window.requestAnimationFrame()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/onmozbeforepaint\"><code>window.onmozbeforepaint</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"Returns the time, in milliseconds since the epoch, at which animations started now should be considered to have started. This value should be used instead of, for example, Date.now(), because this value will be the same for all animations started in this window during this refresh interval, allowing them to remain in sync with one another.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Animation.startTime","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Animation.startTime","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Window.mozAnimationStartTime","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window.mozAnimationStartTime","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/animation/starttime","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/animation/starttime/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation","title":"Animation"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Animation/startTime","title":"window.mozAnimationStartTime"}],"pageTitle":"window.mozAnimationStartTime - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}